'''Buḥejjar''' d yiwet taɣiwant n twilayt n [[Ṭṭaref]], deg wenẓul n twilayt-a yerna teqreb tamdint n [[Ɛennaba]]. Deg 2008, ɣur-es azal n 20,215 imezdaɣen, yerna mechuret s lluzinat i yellan deg-s am tid n Arcelor-Mittal i yeldan deg 2001 maca awanak adzayri isaɣ-iten tikkelt nniḍen deg useggwas [[2013]]. 

